OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,FA pub manager and a store owner in
OL,7,FGuernsey say businesses are losing
OL,8,Fsignificant income and customers
OL,9,Ffollowing multiple main road closures
OL,10,Fthis year.
OL,12,FIt comes after Forest Road and nearby
OL,13,Froutes have been closed for 37 days in
OL,14,F2025 so far.
