OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,FPaul Wickner, manager of The Deerhound
OL,7,FPub, says it has lost #9,000 because
OL,8,Fof the disruption and with the latest
OL,9,Froadworks set to last 26 days in
OL,10,FSeptember, he adds: "We are lucky we
OL,11,Fhave a good reputation with dinners,
OL,12,Fespecially, but certainly breakfast
OL,13,Fand lunch times have been a disaster.
OL,15,F"This is the main route between the
OL,16,FAirport and St Peter Port, so it's
OL,17,Faffecting tourism, it's a negative
OL,18,Fexperience for those arriving. But
OL,19,Fultimately, it's just figuring out
OL,20,Fwhere we at one day to the next."
