OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,FPaul continues: "It's the confusion
OL,7,Ffrom a guest's point of view, which
OL,8,Fdirection do they need to come from.
OL,9,FThere is also probably not the best
OL,10,Fsignage in terms of getting people
OL,11,Faround to this point as well.
OL,13,F"If there is significant work that
OL,14,Fneeds to take place, it's about
OL,15,Fgetting it all done in a shorter
OL,16,Fperiod of time.
