OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,F"There are periods of the year when we
OL,7,Fchoose to close the roads, which need
OL,8,Fto be considered. For example, access
OL,9,Fon this road has been denied at the
OL,10,Fbeginning of the holiday period and
OL,11,Fthen towards the end.
OL,13,F"Perhaps we could have had a look at
OL,14,Fthe quieter months, late October
OL,15,Fonwards, where there isn't the tourist
OL,16,Ftrade to fall back on."
