OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,F"They (The States of Guernsey) need to
OL,7,Ftalk to everybody involved and try and
OL,8,Fget things done in one go, the
OL,9,Felectrics and the water agencies, for
OL,10,Fexample.
OL,12,F"We should be closing the road once
OL,13,Fand getting everything done instead of
OL,14,Fmultiple closures."
OL,16,FWhen have the roads been closed so far
OL,17,Fthis year?
OL,19,FOwner of Forest Stores, Keith
OL,20,FBienvenu, says his business has also
OL,21,Fbeen significantly affected.
