OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,FHe explains: "It does have a
OL,7,Fconsiderable impact on the business.
OL,9,F"We are about 200 customers a day
OL,10,Fdown. Some people are disgruntled
OL,11,Fabout it - they say it's not the first
OL,12,Ftime this has happened, and the
OL,13,Fdiversion signs aren't always clear
OL,14,Fabout what the diversion actually is."
