OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,FIn response, the States of Guernsey's
OL,7,FTraffic and Highway Services says:
OL,8,F"Proactively resurfacing our roads is
OL,9,Fpart of responsible management of our
OL,10,Fhighways, in which we are committed to
OL,11,Fmaintaining a high standard across the
OL,12,Froad network.
OL,14,F"By acting now, we avoid more costly
OL,15,Fand disruptive repairs in the future.
OL,16,FWe're also taking the opportunity to
OL,17,Finstall several pedestrian crossings
OL,18,Fto improve accessibility.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
