OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,F"We fully recognise the importance of
OL,7,Fthis road to local businesses and the
OL,8,Fwider community, and as a result, our
OL,9,Fcontractor has been working seven days
OL,10,Fa week to complete this project as
OL,11,Fsoon as possible.
OL,13,F"Once complete, the road will be
OL,14,Fprotected by a three-year embargo on
OL,15,Ffurther works, except in emergencies,
OL,16,Fensuring long-term benefit.
