OL,3,CRepeat roadworks causing major losses,
OL,4,Cbusinesses say
OL,6,F"In the lead-up to resurfacing,
OL,7,Futility providers are encouraged to
OL,8,Fcomplete any necessary works, which is
OL,9,Fwhy there has been previous work in
OL,10,Fthe area.
OL,12,F"We always work closely with utilities
OL,13,Fto coordinate their works where
OL,14,Fpossible, which is why there's often
OL,15,Fmore than one utility working in an
OL,16,Farea at any one time to avoid multiple
OL,17,Fclosures. This coordination helps
OL,18,Favoid repeated closures and further
OL,19,Fdisruption."
